Package FOMS.order_manager

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddPaymentMethod
    The AddPaymentMethod class provides functionality to add new payment methods to the system.
    AddRemovePayment
    The AddRemovePayment class provides a user interface for adding or removing payment methods in the FOMS.
    CartManager
    The CartManager class manages the shopping cart in FOMS.
    CollectOrderPage
    The CollectOrderPage class manages the interface for collecting orders within FOMS.
    GetPaymentMethods
    The GetPaymentMethods class provides functionalities for retrieving and displaying available payment methods from a file within FOMS.
    Order
    The Order class represents an order within FOMS.
    OrderItem
    Represents an item within an order in FOMS.
    OrderManager
    Manages orders placed by customers, including creation, status tracking, and persistence.
    RemovePaymentMethod
    Provides functionality to remove a payment method from the list of available payment methods.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OrderStatus
    Enumerates the possible statuses of an order.
